# Phase 12.9 + 13.0 — Save/Export/Packaging + Modding/Content Pack System

## Summary

This implementation adds two major layers to the RPG system:

### Phase 12.9 — Save / Export / Packaging Layer
- **Package I/O module** (`src/app/rpg/packaging/`) for exporting/importing RPG sessions
- **Package manifest** with version, title, description, creator metadata
- **Package contains**: simulation state, presentation state, character cards, world summary, visual registry
- **Bounded payloads** with character/asset limits to prevent abuse
- **Normalization** on import to ensure consistent state

### Phase 13.0 — Modding / Extension System / Content Pack Pipeline
- **Content pack module** (`src/app/rpg/modding/`) for deterministic, data-only content packs
- **Pack types**: character packs, scenario packs, world packs, visual style packs
- **Pack operations**: list, preview, apply
- **Explicit application only** — no hidden pack execution
- **Visual defaults** can be applied from packs

